# Code Review

Every pull request should verify:

Architecture

Naming

Performance

Accessibility

Testing

Security

Documentation

---

# Review Questions

Does it follow Feature Architecture?

Does it reuse components?

Does it use design tokens?

Does it introduce duplication?

Does it reduce maintainability?

---

# Rejections

Reject PRs that:

Duplicate code

Hardcode colors

Bypass repositories

Mix business logic into widgets

Break accessibility

Reduce testability

---

# Cursor Instructions

Review generated code against these standards before considering it complete.